com.ai.ASTCells

Class IFASTCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ai.ASTCells.AbstractASTCell
      • com.ai.ASTCells.IFASTCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTCell

    public class IFASTCell
extends AbstractASTCell
    Node in the #AST structure representing an if statement. The only trinary node in the Syntax tree structure. Holds a statement ASTCell for the condition to enter the thenClause, a block ASTCell to execute if the clause condition was met. and a block to execute if there is an else statement. If there is no else statement, This block contains the NilASTCell
    Author:
    Martin Tice
